title: How many songs has Bob Dylan written that has the word 'alley' in it? - Quora

response.answer_text: That’s a really funny question. Bob Dylan has a ton of songs so I doubt anyone is going to go through them all to find an accurate answer for you. Two or three come to mind immediately but I’m sure there’s a bunch more. The three that I can think of are: Subterranean Homesick BluesBob Dylan’s 115th DreamStuck Inside of Mobile with the Memphis Blues AgainEdit- I thought of one more- “Tombstone Blues”. That should’ve been the first one I thought of since it’s in the chorus. lol
